<HEADLINE>
FT  25 OCT 93 / Romania controls
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Romanian Prime Minister Nicolae Vacaroiu has ordered price controls and
curbs on imports in a new blow to economic reforms, Reuter reports.
</TEXT>
