European Parliament (Permanent seat)
MUNICH
European Patent Office
LISBON
Bidding form Environment Agency
MADRID
Bidding form Environment Agency
BARCELONA
Bidding for Medicines Evaluation Agency
LONDON
Most likely site for Medicines Evaluation Agency
LONDON
European Bank for reconstruction and Development (EBRD)
COPENHAGEN
Bidding for Environment Agency, Trade Mark Office, Medicines Evaluation
Agency
THE HAGUE
Most likely site for Europol Drugs Agency
BERLIN
Bidding for Environment Agency, Foundation for Training
LUXEMBOURG
Bidding for Trade Mark Office
FRANKFURT
Most likely site for European Monetary Institute (EMI), forerunner
to European Central Bank
</TEXT>
