<HEADLINE>
FT  23 OCT 93 / Economic Diary
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
TODAY: World law conference begins in Manila and continues until October 29.
SUNDAY: Dalai Lama begins visit to France, until November 15; parliamentary
elections in Liechtenstein; Arab states meet on Israel boycott.
MONDAY: Canadian general election; German CPI (regions, possible); Ecofin
Luxembourg; interim results - BET.
