parliament session in Strasbourg; Dutch prime minister Ruud Lubbers begins
three-day visit to India; Australian prime minister Paul Keating visits
Jakarta for talks with president Suharto ahead of meeting in Seattle of
Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation (APEC) forum (until October 28); final
results - Data General.
